{
  "stem": "5259.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we stood up, maybe in our-- because of our features.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the-- the Asiats are different than we.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They have different features of face.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they are more like Mongols.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we have normal-- you know, normal faces, like white people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They knew, probably.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There-- And I think it was in 1944 that my father was taken to a labor camp in Russia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They took all the men.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I think it was at the time of Leningrad-- of Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they took all the men away, not only Jewish men, but all the men.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he was taken to a labor camp, again, somewhere in Siberia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't remember where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he stayed there for many months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I think till, almost the war was, was finished.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Almost, a few months before.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And again, we [? struck ?] our poverty, because it was impossible to sell anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we were on our own.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "My mother was working, but couldn't provide us with enough money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We didn't-- I cannot say that, that we were afraid of our lives.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
